psalm.text:
[[Ps 17,1]]Hear, O LORD, a just suit;
attend to my outcry;
hearken to my prayer from lips without deceit.

[[Ps 17,2]]From you let my judgment come; 
Your eyes behold what is right.
[[Ps 17,3]]Though you test my heart, searching it in the night, 
though you try me with fire, you shall find no malice in me.

[[Ps 17,6]]I call upon you, for you will answer me, O God;
incline your ear to me; hear my word.
[[Ps 17,7]]Show your wondrous mercies, 
O savior of those who flee from their foes
